Package Application

This package contains all the classes related to the application layer

The main function of this layer is to translate tasks and results to something the user can understand

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    DeleteCollaboration
    Contains the view and the methods to delete a collaboration
    ExpertsManagement
    Contains the view and the all the methods related to the Experts Management submenu
    GUI
    This is the Graphical User Interface of the application, all the others views are called within this class.
    InsertCollaboration
    Contains the view and all the methods to insert a collaboration
    ManageByCase
    Contains the view and all the methods to manage the collaborations with a case code given.
    ManageByExpert
    Contains the view and all the methods to manage the collaborations with an expert code given
    NewCase
    Contains the User Interface for managing the cases and all the methods to do so
    NewExpert
    Contains the view and all the methods to add and remove experts from the DB
